Author: unityproject_ico
Title: Ways on how to effectively protect our systems from intrusion
Body: Thanks for the encouragement. We're really excited about the project, and are confident in our vision.  We do indeed have a signature campaign! All information on our bounty program can be found here: https://www.onewed.com/unitycoin-bounty-program/  Signature codes can be found on pages 9 - 13.  Quote from: spiderlee on October 20, 2017, 12:14:06 AM why is that you don't have social media bounty  We are at this time undecided on whether or not we would like to provide a social media bounty. However, we do have a significant portion of UNTY set aside for additional rewards. If we get enough enthusiasm for a social media bounty, we will consider including it in our Guidelines document (check the link above) as an additional reward.
